<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Pinball — Games Landing</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<style>
  :root {
    --chrome: #c9d1e0;
    --neon-pink: #ff3ea5;
    --neon-cyan: #36e3ff;
    --neon-amber: #ffd23a;
    --ink: #07070d;
    --rail: #1a1c2c;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% -20%, #2b0d3a 0%, #0a0612 55%, #000 100%);
    color: #f1f1ff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  }
  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .scoreboard {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    background: #0a0014;
    border: 3px solid var(--chrome);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 16px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.45),
      0 0 24px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.35);
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    color: var(--neon-amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, var(--neon-pink) 60%, #6a0033 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.35);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .tag { color: var(--neon-cyan); letter-spacing: 0.3em; font-size: 13px; }
  nav { text-align: center; margin: 20px 0 0; }
  nav a {
    color: var(--neon-cyan);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--neon-cyan);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .card {
    position: relative;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, #2a0028 0%, #0c0410 70%),
      var(--ink);
    border: 3px solid var(--chrome);
    border-radius: 28px 28px 80px 80px / 28px 28px 120px 120px;
    padding: 24px 22px 32px;
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 30px rgba(54, 227, 255, 0.18),
      0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6),
      0 0 30px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.18);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 0 30px rgba(54, 227, 255, 0.3),
      0 24px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
      0 0 50px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.4);
  }
  .bumpers {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 12px 12px auto 12px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .bumper {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff, var(--neon-amber) 60%, #6b3a00);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--neon-amber);
  }
  .bumper.c { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff, var(--neon-cyan) 60%, #003744); box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--neon-cyan); }
  .bumper.p { background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #fff, var(--neon-pink) 60%, #4a0026); box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--neon-pink); }
  .shot {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0028, #00131a);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    margin: 12px 0 18px;
  }
  .title {
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    color: var(--neon-amber);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 210, 58, 0.55);
  }
  .prompt {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #d6d6ee;
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 84px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .play {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--neon-pink), #b8005c);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 2px solid var(--chrome);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255, 62, 165, 0.65), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .play:hover { filter: brightness(1.15); }
  .flippers {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -18px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 14px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .flip {
    width: 80px; height: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--chrome), #6b7286);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  .flip.l { transform: rotate(20deg); transform-origin: left center; }
  .flip.r { transform: rotate(-20deg); transform-origin: right center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="scoreboard">▸ FLIPPER FUN ◂ TILT WARNING ◂ MULTI-BALL</div>
    <h1>Pinball</h1>
    <div class="tag">— Six original tables —</div>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← All themes</a></nav>
  </header>

  <main class="grid">
    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper"></span><span class="bumper c"></span><span class="bumper p"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/chrome-arcade-pinball"><img class="shot" src="https://chrome-arcade-pinball--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Neon Flippers</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Two flippers, three glowing bumpers, plunger launches the ball. Bumpers ricochet for points; gutter drains. Animated digital score readout, neon chrome aesthetic.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/chrome-arcade-pinball">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper c"></span><span class="bumper p"></span><span class="bumper"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/orbital-arcade"><img class="shot" src="https://orbital-arcade--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Galaxy Drift</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Space pinball: ball is a glowing comet, bumpers are planets, flippers are solar panels. Tilt warning if jostled. Persistent high-score table over starfield.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/orbital-arcade">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper p"></span><span class="bumper"></span><span class="bumper c"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/turbo-bumper"><img class="shot" src="https://turbo-bumper--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Bumper Blitz</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Speed pinball with shrinking timer. Three flippers in a triangle, heavy bumpers, multi-ball unlocks at 1000 points. Cracked-glass flash at milestones.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/turbo-bumper">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper"></span><span class="bumper p"></span><span class="bumper c"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/buccaneer-pinball"><img class="shot" src="https://buccaneer-pinball--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Pirate Cove</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Cannon plunger, treasure-chest bumpers, a kraken target that opens its jaws for a jackpot. Pieces-of-eight unlock multi-ball. Wooden plank borders.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/buccaneer-pinball">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper c"></span><span class="bumper"></span><span class="bumper p"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/melody-flipper"><img class="shot" src="https://melody-flipper--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Jukebox Juke</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Bumpers play synth notes when struck, building a melody. Multipliers when hits land on rhythm. Retro vinyl visuals and neon jukebox borders.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/melody-flipper">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <div class="bumpers"><span class="bumper p"></span><span class="bumper c"></span><span class="bumper"></span></div>
      <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/wrecking-ball-city"><img class="shot" src="https://wrecking-ball-city--jchris.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt=""></a>
      <h2 class="title">Skyline Bash</h2>
      <p class="prompt">Skyscrapers are bumpers, ball is a wrecking ball. Topple buildings for points; they rebuild after ten seconds. Sunset gradient skyline backdrop.</p>
      <a class="play" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/jchris/wrecking-ball-city">▶ Play</a>
      <div class="flippers"><span class="flip l"></span><span class="flip r"></span></div>
    </article>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
